WEBVTT

17:14.899 --> 17:17.560 line:80%
the authorities
usually won't punish them all.

17:18.149 --> 17:20.240 line:80%
Now the whole town is gossiping about me

17:20.240 --> 17:21.540 line:80%
behind my back.

17:22.200 --> 17:24.000 line:80%
I might be able to deal with one of them,

17:24.000 --> 17:25.530 line:80%
but can I deal with them all?
